    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is the absolute pinnacle of automotive care, presenting in true showroom condition. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or blemishes. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, reflecting its history of being exclusively garage-kept and hand-washed. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. All electronic systems, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule. It drives with the tightness and precision of a brand-new vehicle, offering a quiet, powerful, and vibration-free experience. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a collector-grade example that has been pampered by a single meticulous owner. No accidents, no smokers, and absolutely no compromises.",
